    <!-- ── 4. BATTLE SYSTEM ── -->
    <div class="doc-section" id="battle">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-num">4</div>
            <div class="section-title">Battle System</div>
        </div>
        <p class="section-text">
            Battles are narrative-driven &mdash; you'll see a story of what happened, not raw numbers.
            The outcome is determined by your Digimon's <strong>level</strong>, <strong>type advantage</strong>, and a bit of luck.
        </p>

        <div class="info-card red">
            <div class="card-title">Battle Mechanics</div>
            <div class="card-text">
                <strong>Level Matters:</strong> A higher-level Digimon deals more damage and has more health.<br>
                <strong>Type Advantage:</strong> Some types are super effective against others (2x damage).<br>
                <strong>Narrative Log:</strong> Battles describe what your Digimon does &mdash; fire blasts, ice storms, shadow strikes &mdash; and explain <strong>why</strong> the winner won.<br>
                <strong>Winner Reward:</strong> The winning Digimon earns <strong>+25 XP</strong>.<br>
                <strong>Max 10 Rounds:</strong> If neither Digimon falls, the one with more remaining strength wins.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card cyan">
            <div class="card-title">Example Battle Narrative</div>
            <div class="card-text" style="font-style:italic; color:#6688aa;">
                "Agumon (Lv.5 Fire) faces off against Gabumon (Lv.3 Ice)!<br><br>
                Agumon unleashes a blazing fireball! The type advantage is overwhelming!<br>
                Gabumon blasts a frozen beam... but the attack barely scratches the surface.<br>
                Agumon breathes searing flames! A critical weakness is exposed!<br><br>
                Agumon claims victory thanks to higher level (Lv.5 vs Lv.3) and Fire type advantage over Ice!
                Gabumon retreats to recover."
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="digi-showcase">
            <div class="digi-card" style="border-color:#ff333644;">
                <img src="/digimon/child/Agumon.gif" alt="Agumon">
                <div class="digi-name">Agumon</div>
                <div class="digi-stage" style="color:#ff3366;">Fire Attacker</div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;color:#ff6600;font-family:'Orbitron',monospace;font-size:24px;font-weight:900;">VS</div>
            <div class="digi-card" style="border-color:#00ccff44;">
                <img src="/digimon/child/Betamon.gif" alt="Betamon">
                <div class="digi-name">Betamon</div>
                <div class="digi-stage" style="color:#00ccff;">Water Defender</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

