            <div class="section-num">5</div>
            <div class="section-title">Type System</div>
        </div>
        <p class="section-text">
            There are <strong>14 Digimon types</strong>. Each type has strengths and weaknesses against other types.
            Understanding the type chart is key to winning battles.
        </p>

        <div class="type-grid">
            <div class="type-chip" style="background:#F0803088;border:1px solid #F08030;">Fire</div>
            <div class="type-chip" style="background:#6890F088;border:1px solid #6890F0;">Water</div>
            <div class="type-chip" style="background:#78C85088;border:1px solid #78C850;">Nature</div>
            <div class="type-chip" style="background:#F8D03088;border:1px solid #F8D030;color:#000;">Electric</div>
            <div class="type-chip" style="background:#98D8D888;border:1px solid #98D8D8;color:#000;">Ice</div>
            <div class="type-chip" style="background:#E0C06888;border:1px solid #E0C068;color:#000;">Earth</div>
