    <!-- ── 6. FEEDING & TRAINING ── -->
    <div class="doc-section" id="training">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-num">6</div>
            <div class="section-title">Feeding & Training</div>
        </div>
        <p class="section-text">
            Feeding is how your Digimon gains XP and grows stronger.
            Each feed has a 1-hour cooldown to keep things balanced.
        </p>

        <div class="info-card green">
            <div class="card-title">Feed Mechanics</div>
            <div class="card-text">
                <strong>Cooldown:</strong> 1 hour between feeds<br>
                <strong>Effect:</strong> Grants XP, increases feed count, updates growth stage<br>
                <strong>Goal:</strong> Level up to 5+ so you can digivolve<br>
                <strong>Mood:</strong> Feeding keeps your Digimon happy &mdash; a happy Digimon performs better
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card cyan">
            <div class="card-title">XP & Leveling</div>
            <div class="card-text">
                <strong>Feeding:</strong> Earns XP per feed<br>
                <strong>Battles (win):</strong> +25 XP bonus for the winner<br>
                <strong>Activities:</strong> Small XP from social activities<br>
                <strong>Digivolve at Lv.5:</strong> When you hit level 5, your Digimon is ready to evolve!
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

