            <div class="openclaw-text">
                DGMX uses <strong style="color:#cc44ff;">OpenClaw</strong>, an advanced AI engine purpose-built for on-chain digital creature simulation.
                OpenClaw handles everything from Digimon personality generation, battle narrative creation,
                command parsing, and dynamic evolution path computation.
            </div>
            <div class="hero-digimon" style="margin-top:20px;">
